## Common Causes of High Usage

| Cause | Signs | Solution |
|-------|-------|----------|
| HVAC running constantly | Spike matches hot/cold weather | Check thermostat, service AC |
| Water heater | Consistent high baseline | Lower temp to 120°F, insulate |
| Pool pump | Seasonal pattern | Reduce run time, variable speed |
| Old refrigerator | 24/7 draw | Replace (rebates available!) |
| Space heaters | Winter spike | Seal drafts, use central heat |
| Hot tub | High continuous use | Cover when not in use |

